 * This is a simple FAT32 driver.
 *
 * Created for Hackndev; Intended for the Palm LifeDrive.
 * Meant to be easily ported to other devices.
 *
 * Replace drive.c functions with other, direct-access functions
 * if you want to access a different FAT32 filesystem.
 *
 * drive.c has low-level drive-access functions, such as readsector
 *
 * fat.c holds FAT32-specific functions, like readfile
 *
